trans-unit.source: Represents the overflow section of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Representa a seção de estouro de um objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel" />.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel> and is not intended to be used independently.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é usada por <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel> e não se destina a ser usado de forma independente.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" />.

trans-unit.source: The size that the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" /> needs to position its child elements.
trans-unit.target: O tamanho de que o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" /> precisa para posicionar seus elementos filho.

trans-unit.source: Positions and sizes the child elements in this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" />.
trans-unit.target: Posiciona e dimensiona os elementos filho neste <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" />.

trans-unit.source: Measures the child elements in this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" /> in preparation of arranging them during the <see cref="M:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel.ArrangeOverride(System.Windows.Size)" /> pass.
trans-unit.target: Mede os elementos filho neste <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel" /> em preparação para organizá-los durante a passagem de <see cref="M:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarOverflowPanel.ArrangeOverride(System.Windows.Size)" />.
